+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0+
+/*
+ * Surface Fan driver for Surface System Aggregator Module. It provides access
+ * to the fan's rpm through the hwmon system.
+ *
+ * Copyright (C) 2023 Ivor Wanders <ivor@iwanders.net>
+ */
+
